en_230353_0	A successful big onion harvest has been received from the Polonnaruwa district.
en_230353_1	Big onions are mostly cultivated at Elahera area.
en_230353_2	Farmers say that they have commenced harvesting and they are getting a high price of 250 rupees for a kilogram of big onions at present.
en_230353_3	Big onions have been cultivated at Saru Bima, Kottapitiya, Athar Gallewa 505 and 506 areas in Elahera.
en_230353_4	Farmers say that they receive a harvest of 4,000 to 5,000 kilograms of big onions per an acre.
